VEERG_4_5_1_1__7_VolatileSolidsTransferredStage2_LatexEquation
  =LAMBDA("VST_{ijm,T=2}=VS_{j}\times FVS_{jm,T=1}\times(1-VSL_{m,T=1})");

VEERG_4_5_1_1__7_VolatileSolidsTransferredStage2_Arguments
